articles.author: Greta Cross
articles.title: Australian journalist shot with nonlethal bullet while reporting on LA protests - USA Today
articles.description: Australian journalist Lauren Tomasi was shot in the leg by a rubber bullet while reporting on the immigration raids in Los Angeles on Sunday, June 8.
articles.content:
An Australian journalist was shot with a rubber bullet by an officer while covering protests in Los Angeles over the weekend, according to her media outlet.
